{
  "stem": "14715.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it was-- we couldn't-- if you break a window, and we lost a ball, we had to pay for the window to get back the ball.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So it wasn't good.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then the other thing, we didn't have the time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "As I mentioned it to you, we went to cheder and then public school, that there wasn't much time to play outside except Sunday.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I-- first of all I don't know if my father was interested at all.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was too young to get in in those things.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I did not belong to any organizations.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Ah, well, our goals, some of them went to higher education, which was like gymnasium, but it was high school.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But you had to pay for it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I think the majority of the people didn't have the pay to pay for it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I remember my goal was just to go to gymnasium because my father, as I say, was in business.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Although we were not rich, but I think we could afford to send the children to the higher education.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And probably take on the profession what my father had.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Personally, I didn't, experience it because I didn't mix with any other nationalities.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I had stories.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I tell them that we were not very well liked.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Poland as a whole was very anti-Semitic.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I remember when Pilsudski, which was the president, died.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They used to say that he was a grandfather of the Jews.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And in that time it really started problems with slaughtering of the kosher cows.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They used to stay outside Jewish stores with signs, 'don't buy from Jews.' At 1933, '34, anti-Semitism really came to fact.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
